caller_intent: Manolo is seeking assistance to complete a document he did not receive via email, which is required to retain a discount. He plans to visit the office in person tomorrow to address this.
resolution_steps: Agent explains the document is necessary to maintain the discount and clarifies it must be completed by the caller.
Agent offers to help Manolo complete the document in person at the office.
Agent suggests contacting the company to resend the email if Manolo did not receive it.
Agent confirms Manolo's plan to visit the office tomorrow and agrees to meet at 11:30 AM.
Agent notes alternative assistance options if Manolo cannot attend.
knowledge_required: Understanding of document requirements for discounts
Process for resending documents via company systems
Office location and availability for in-person assistance
summary: Manolo needs to complete a document to retain a discount but did not receive the email. The agent explains the necessity, offers in-person help at the office tomorrow, and confirms a meeting time. The caller agrees to attend, with backup assistance options available if needed.
